<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>FAQs - EliteEscapes</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #FFFFF0;
            color: #013220;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #013220;
            color: #FFFFF0;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li {
            margin: 0 15px;
        }

        .navbar nav ul li a {
            color: #FFFFF0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .faq-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #FFFFF0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .faq-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .faq-title h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        .faq-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #013220;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .faq-item h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .faq-item p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #013220;
            color: #FFFFF0;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer .social-icons {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer .social-icons a {
            color: #FFFFF0;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer .social-icons a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">EliteEscapes</div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="faq-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="faq-title">
                <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What are the check-in and check-out times?</h3>
                <p>Our standard check-in time is 3:00 PM, and check-out is at 12:00 PM. Early check-in and late check-out are subject to availability and may incur additional charges.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Do you offer free Wi-Fi?</h3>
                <p>Yes, complimentary Wi-Fi is available in all our hotels for our guests.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What is your cancellation policy?</h3>
                <p>The cancellation policy varies by booking type and rate. Please refer to your booking confirmation for specific details.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Are pets allowed in the hotels?</h3>
                <p>Some of our properties are pet-friendly. Please contact the specific hotel for their pet policy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Do you provide airport transportation?</h3>
                <p>Yes, airport transportation is available at select locations. Additional charges may apply.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2024 EliteEscapes | All Rights Reserved</p>
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
